info.title: PIA Platform API
info.description: API for managing AI agents, calls, phone numbers, and more.

post.description:
Create a new AI agent with the provided configuration.

This endpoint allows you to create a new AI agent by specifying its properties,
including LLM, TTS, and STT configurations. The created agent will be associated
with the authenticated user.

- **agent**: The configuration details for the new AI agent.

get.description:
Retrieve details of a specific AI agent.

This endpoint fetches the complete configuration and details of an AI agent
identified by its unique agent_id. Only agents created by the authenticated
user can be retrieved.

- **agent_id**: The unique identifier of the AI agent to retrieve.
